## App Store Release Checklist

Before public App Store release:

- Publish this policy at the public Privacy Policy URL entered in App Store Connect.
- Verify the URL loads over HTTPS without authentication.
- Keep this policy synchronized with App Store privacy labels.
- Recheck this policy whenever Health, iCloud, notifications, widgets, exports, support, analytics, StoreKit, or data-sharing behavior changes.

